## MongoDB
## Replace <db_password> with your actual password (do NOT commit secrets)
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://arleettt1_db_user:<db_password>@cluster0.z7qq1ne.mongodb.net/?appName=Cluster0

## JWT (Access + Refresh)
## IMPORTANT: Use strong secrets in production. Do NOT commit real secrets.
JWT_SECRET=change-me-dev
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=change-me-refresh-dev
